00:09:25.350 --> 00:09:27.600
d- UNK efsher iz dos gevezn akht tog

00:09:27.600 --> 00:09:29.590
o- bin ikh dort gevezn in di politsey

00:09:30.370 --> 00:09:32.490
kh'zol hobn di UNK MLECZARNIA

00:09:33.137 --> 00:09:38.193
UNK dort in UNK MLECZARNIA iz gekumen tsu forn a vogn. s'iz gekumen tsu forn a familye

00:09:38.301 --> 00:09:40.691
mit fir, fir perzonen

00:09:41.153 --> 00:09:43.374
un ⟨dort⟩ bay di drotn iz geshtanen a vogn

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:44.685
un der

00:09:44.685 --> 00:09:46.335
Dovid, der Dovid GETLER

00:09:46.335 --> 00:09:47.575
vos er iz gekumen fun

00:09:47.575 --> 00:09:49.495
fun di Varshe

00:09:49.742 --> 00:09:52.186
iz dort gevezn, un m'hot gefirt, farshteystu

00:09:52.186 --> 00:09:55.609
m'hot genumen di mentshn, aroysgefirt, m'hot UNK avekgeganen

00:09:56.155 --> 00:09:58.624
iz er avekgeforn keyn Varshe, zenen zey geforn

00:09:58.624 --> 00:10:00.864
un m'hot genumen batsolt gelt fun di mentshn

00:10:00.864 --> 00:10:04.434
iz gevezn a sh- a ofn, ofn shmugl fun, mit di daytshn, hot men genumen gelt.

00:10:04.997 --> 00:10:07.525
mit eyn molt efsher, s'hot, ikh hob gehat sluzhbe

00:10:07.525 --> 00:10:09.888
fun, lomir zogn fun, fun akhte

00:10:09.888 --> 00:10:12.335
biz fire. fun fire hot gehat UNK a tsveyter

00:10:12.335 --> 00:10:14.930
bin ikh dort gevezn, hot gedoyert efsher fir sho

00:10:15.291 --> 00:10:17.276
iz der vogn tsurik gekumen tsu forn.

00:10:17.383 --> 00:10:19.857
m'hot mitgebrengt fir mayster tsurik

00:10:20.050 --> 00:10:21.107
ale toyte.

00:10:22.716 --> 00:10:26.088
farshteyst? zey hobn tsugenumen dos gelt. zey hobn undz UNK arayngebrengt in di geto.

00:10:26.088 --> 00:10:27.503
ikh hob dos gezen

00:10:28.302 --> 00:10:30.490
zog ikh do "ikh vil nisht, vayl ikh hob moyre tsu geyn"

00:10:31.052 --> 00:10:32.328
ahin, aher

00:10:32.571 --> 00:10:35.383
bin ikh gevoyr gevorn UNK ⟨bin nisht keyn⟩ frisher

00:10:35.710 --> 00:10:39.889
az undzer, fun undzer grupe, fun lines hatsedek, iz g- er iz do geshtorbn

00:10:39.962 --> 00:10:41.596
heyst er ⟨CZARNOBRODA⟩.

00:10:41.596 --> 00:10:43.483
er iz geven der prezes fun di yugnt.

00:10:44.653 --> 00:10:47.583
er iz gevorn der sekreter bay dokter ⟨Shiker⟩

00:10:47.843 --> 00:10:50.385
fun krankn⟨HAUS⟩, fun UNK GESUNDHEIT

00:10:51.100 --> 00:10:56.122
nu, bin ikh d- gelo- UNK m'iz geven tsunezamen, bin ikh gelofn tsun im, zog ikh "Khenek

00:10:56.145 --> 00:10:57.922
vos tut zikh do? ikh ken nisht."

00:10:57.922 --> 00:10:59.429
zogt er "veystu vos?

00:10:59.706 --> 00:11:04.087
me ⟨grindet⟩, hot gegrindet yetst UNK er heyst a SANITARNA KOMISJA.

00:11:04.650 --> 00:11:06.765
du vest vern ⟨in⟩ SANITARNA KOMISJA

00:11:06.765 --> 00:11:08.221
un d'vest geyn in shpitol arayn."

00:11:08.498 --> 00:11:12.086
dort iz optsuesn, un dort iz nisht UNK gesheftn

00:11:12.261 --> 00:11:14.972
er hot mikh bashtetikt. ikh hob gekrign a, a PRZYDZIAL

00:11:15.028 --> 00:11:16.231
in shpitol arayn.

00:11:16.231 --> 00:11:17.908
ikh bin gekumen in shpitol arayn

00:11:17.998 --> 00:11:21.404
hob ikh gekrign a PRZYDZ- dort geven tsvey UNK. eyner iz UNK

00:11:21.404 --> 00:11:24.518
OBERDOKTOR FUCHS vos er iz do do haynt, do in ⟨LANDRES⟩

00:11:24.518 --> 00:11:27.478
profesor, un er UNK operirt froyen

00:11:27.478 --> 00:11:29.338
far kinder mit hipnoz

00:11:29.411 --> 00:11:32.811
er, un a geviser ABRAMOVITSH vos shraybt di tsaytung

00:11:32.811 --> 00:11:36.892
di bikher ⟨bashribn⟩ im. host nisht gehert ABRAMOVITSH? er shraybt fun di Lodzher geto

00:11:36.898 --> 00:11:38.174
vu er iz ⟨dokh⟩ gevezn

00:11:38.569 --> 00:11:41.381
er iz gevezn, un mir hobn getoysht zikh dray shift

00:11:41.404 --> 00:11:42.444
hot men gehat.

00:11:42.653 --> 00:11:44.480
ikh hob gehat fir un tsvantsik sho

00:11:44.480 --> 00:11:46.404
UNK andere fir un tsvantsik sho

00:11:46.404 --> 00:11:48.319
hot men mir gebrengt, dort hot men gebrengt

00:11:48.319 --> 00:11:49.261
kranke

00:11:49.538 --> 00:11:51.416
un m'hot gebrengt tseshlogene

00:11:51.416 --> 00:11:53.565
vos di ⟨KRIPO⟩ hot genumen

00:11:53.622 --> 00:11:55.219
farshteyst? un hot tsehakt

00:11:55.326 --> 00:12:00.635
der ⟨KRIPO⟩ iz gevezn, der sh- der hekhster shef fun di ⟨KRIPO⟩ iz gevezn SIEWERT

00:12:01.772 --> 00:12:06.114
UND der tsveyter iz gevezn NEUMANN, un der driter iz gevezn

00:12:06.114 --> 00:12:07.166
⟨SUTER⟩.

00:12:07.780 --> 00:12:10.223
vos hobn zey getun? yidishe slikheners

00:12:10.223 --> 00:12:13.066
hobn oyfgegebn az der mentsh hot bahaltn in di geto

00:12:13.066 --> 00:12:15.975
⟨iz⟩ gekumen tsu geyn, un m'hot tseshlogn un tsehakt "gib op"

00:12:16.065 --> 00:12:19.165
un m'hot opgegebn. UNK a sakh zenen nebekh avekgefaln

00:12:19.165 --> 00:12:20.815
mayn eygener bruder oykhet.

00:12:20.925 --> 00:12:22.539
ahin aher, azoy

00:12:22.697 --> 00:12:25.340
hot men gebrengt tseshlogene, tsehakte in

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:26.820
in shpitol

00:12:26.820 --> 00:12:29.014
un mir zenen gevezn di ⟨akhtung⟩ geber

00:12:29.014 --> 00:12:31.095
farshteystu? in shpitol

00:12:32.046 --> 00:12:35.055
m'hot gebrengt eyner vos er iz geven Leybl MINCBERG. er iz gevezn

00:12:35.055 --> 00:12:37.811
der senator in poylishe regirung

00:12:38.273 --> 00:12:40.309
zayn eydem heyst RADZINER.

00:12:41.040 --> 00:12:44.915
er iz dort gekumen tseshlogn un tsehakt. dos iz geven geferlekh.

00:12:45.428 --> 00:12:50.040
farshteystu, un undz hot men gemuzt akhtung gebn az khas vekholile zol nisht pasirn im epes.

00:12:50.040 --> 00:12:53.508
ikh bin geven bay der operatsye. der dokter UNK hot operirt UNK im.

00:12:53.508 --> 00:12:55.330
kurts tsu di zakh, farshteystu

00:12:55.330 --> 00:12:57.605
mit eyn molt hot men gebrengt a yid

00:12:58.641 --> 00:12:59.988
ikh vil nisht zogn dem nomen

00:12:59.988 --> 00:13:01.152
m'hot gebrengt a yid

00:13:01.152 --> 00:13:05.047
vos UNK tsehakt. vos iz gevezn? far vos hot men im gebre- er hot aleynt dertseylt.

00:13:05.627 --> 00:13:06.988
er iz gevezn

00:13:07.213 --> 00:13:09.075
hot men tsugenumen bay yidn farmegn

00:13:09.075 --> 00:13:12.281
⟨iz⟩ gevezn SIEWERT, der hoypt komisar fun di

00:13:12.281 --> 00:13:13.248
KRIPO

00:13:14.031 --> 00:13:17.113
iz er geven a, a moser far im.

00:13:17.237 --> 00:13:19.661
hot men tsugenumen a groys ⟨farmegn⟩ bar a yid

00:13:20.005 --> 00:13:22.682
hot er im gezogt "far vos darfstu optsugebn dos do?"

00:13:22.705 --> 00:13:26.380
iz er geforn mit im in shtot arayn, un er hot im ba- bahaltn

00:13:26.380 --> 00:13:27.879
in di shtot dos farmegn.

00:13:28.729 --> 00:13:30.123
dos iz geven dos gantse

00:13:30.754 --> 00:13:36.094
un er iz gelign lebn dem. UNK der RADZINER geli- dos iz interesant UNK RADZINER gelign do

00:13:36.094 --> 00:13:37.614
un er iz gelign do.

00:13:38.213 --> 00:13:41.211
shoyn, dos iz dos gantse. mit eyn mol, farshteystu

00:13:41.453 --> 00:13:45.086
kumt der ⟨KRIPO⟩ tsu geyn. me nemt mikh aroyf in di ⟨KRIPO⟩ arayn.

00:13:45.086 --> 00:13:46.036
vos iz?

00:13:46.110 --> 00:13:47.437
er hot gezogt

00:13:48.118 --> 00:13:50.862
az ikh farshteystu hob genumen finef hundert

00:13:50.903 --> 00:13:52.213
D. mark

00:13:52.303 --> 00:13:53.343
bay im

00:13:53.434 --> 00:13:56.448
er zol UNK brengen arayn di froy mit di kinder.

00:13:56.758 --> 00:13:58.798
ikh hob nisht genumen k- keyn gelt

00:13:58.798 --> 00:14:01.028
nor di froy mit di kinder hob ikh arayngelozt.

00:14:01.028 --> 00:14:03.438
s'iz gevezn UNK er hot gegat gangrene shoyn

00:14:03.438 --> 00:14:05.318
hot ongehoybn bay di nakht hot er ongehoybn tsu shrayen

00:14:05.318 --> 00:14:06.948
kolnidre hot er ongehoybn tsu zingen

00:14:06.948 --> 00:14:10.462
m'hot nisht gevust tsi er vet lebn. hot men badarft tsu makhn a transfuzye

00:14:10.630 --> 00:14:12.362
hob ikh nisht getort araynlozn.

00:14:12.688 --> 00:14:14.184
nu, ⟨ober ikh hob ir⟩ arayngelozt.

00:14:14.730 --> 00:14:19.450
UNK gekumen in di ⟨KRIPO⟩, hot mir aroyfgenumen vifl ikh hobn genumen batsolt. m'hot mikh nebekh tseshlogn

00:14:19.450 --> 00:14:21.480
un ikh hob geshrign "ikh hob nisht gornisht genumen"

00:14:21.480 --> 00:14:23.010
ALSO m'hot mikh bafrayt.

00:14:23.033 --> 00:14:24.967
bin ikh gezitsn vayter in shpitol.

00:14:25.092 --> 00:14:28.022
⟨dem⟩ tsveytn tog iz gekumen tsu forn

00:14:28.416 --> 00:14:29.389
di ⟨KRIPO⟩.

00:14:30.036 --> 00:14:33.810
m'hot dem zelbn soykher, dem yid, ikh vil nisht zogn dem nomen

00:14:33.867 --> 00:14:38.467
genumen un UNK mitgenumen UNK undz, mir ts- mikh un mit dem tsveytn

00:14:38.467 --> 00:14:39.517
YAKUBOVITSHn.

00:14:39.517 --> 00:14:41.027
m'hot im aropgefirt oyfn

00:14:41.027 --> 00:14:41.944
oyfn

00:14:42.152 --> 00:14:44.722
ba- UNK gutn ort

00:14:44.722 --> 00:14:46.892
tsum BALUTER plats un oyfn gutn ort arunter

00:14:46.892 --> 00:14:48.152
un zey hobn im dershosn.

00:14:48.177 --> 00:14:50.044
vos hot pasirt? far vos?

00:14:50.556 --> 00:14:51.630
me dertseylt.

00:14:52.260 --> 00:14:55.170
der, farshteystu, der soykher, hot bahaltn ot

00:14:55.170 --> 00:14:55.990
⟨SUTER⟩

00:14:55.990 --> 00:14:57.570
hot tsugenumen a farmegn

00:14:57.570 --> 00:15:00.776
hot er gezogt "far vos geystu opgebn? ikh hob bahaltn far ⟨SUTERn⟩.

00:15:00.816 --> 00:15:02.210
far SK- ⟨SIEWERTn⟩

00:15:02.217 --> 00:15:04.067
ot gibstu op dos do?

00:15:04.292 --> 00:15:08.392
⟨geb im oykh⟩." azoy iz ⟨SUTER⟩ gevoyr gevorn az yener hot genumen, hot men im genumen

00:15:08.392 --> 00:15:11.492
m'hot gezen az UNK hot moyre gehat, ken ⟨oykh⟩ gebn, der hoypt komisar.

00:15:11.492 --> 00:15:13.502
dem hoypt komisar hot men bazaytikt

00:15:13.502 --> 00:15:14.833
un im hot men geshosn.

00:15:16.780 --> 00:15:19.102
shoyn, iz shoyn dos avek ⟨in poter⟩ mit dem

00:15:19.429 --> 00:15:21.510
dernokh dem, farshteyst, azoy vi s'iz gevezn

00:15:21.510 --> 00:15:25.433
UNK ikh vil nisht k- s'iz nokh do tsvey ⟨a mayse⟩ mit az- oykh a, eyner a ⟨ZAWACKI⟩

00:15:25.433 --> 00:15:28.960
vos ikh vil nisht dertseyln. m'hot im gekhapt. er iz antlofn fun shpitol

00:15:28.960 --> 00:15:32.192
kurts tsu der zakh, farshteystu, dernokh kumt UNK tsu mir

00:15:32.192 --> 00:15:33.834
UNK likvidirn di shpitol.

00:15:34.667 --> 00:15:36.163
ikh bin in shpitol

00:15:36.169 --> 00:15:38.148
UNK mit di bilder ⟨zits ikh⟩ in drinen

00:15:38.148 --> 00:15:39.808
iz gekumen tsu forn der

00:15:39.915 --> 00:15:41.968
s- komisar FUCHS

00:15:42.058 --> 00:15:44.848
es iz gekumen tsu forn zayn fartreter, der BOKSER

00:15:44.848 --> 00:15:47.604
⟨KURZON⟩ der BOKSER, gekumen tsu forn

00:15:47.762 --> 00:15:50.518
un s'iz gekumen tsu forn azoy oyfn BALUTER plats

00:15:50.518 --> 00:15:51.924
hobn gearbet mentshn

00:15:52.150 --> 00:15:53.916
zenen gan ongetun privat

00:15:54.985 --> 00:15:57.985
farshteyst? er hot nor gehat ⟨a paske⟩

00:15:57.985 --> 00:15:58.725
do.

00:15:59.305 --> 00:16:01.082
ven s'iz geven UNK

00:16:01.082 --> 00:16:06.994
hot zikh der ⟨SCHWIND⟩ un der ⟨NEUMANN⟩ un der ⟨MEIER⟩ un der UNK un an- UNK

00:16:07.337 --> 00:16:08.481
⟨ADOLFSOHN⟩

00:16:08.481 --> 00:16:11.701
ale d- ongetun di, di milter

00:16:11.701 --> 00:16:14.391
un zey zenen ganen bay di UNK mit di mentshn. s'iz nisht gekumen

00:16:14.391 --> 00:16:15.831
di zelner fun di shtot

00:16:15.831 --> 00:16:18.581
nor zey di fun BALUTER plats, zey hobn dos gefirt.

00:16:18.581 --> 00:16:19.438
mit ⟨FUCHS⟩n

00:16:19.438 --> 00:16:22.408
un mit, mit UNK zayn fartreter, mit dem BOKSER

00:16:22.862 --> 00:16:24.493
un ikh hob dort gezen

00:16:24.550 --> 00:16:27.130
keyner hot nisht gekent zen. do iz geven nebekh eydes

00:16:27.130 --> 00:16:28.580
vos zey hobn gezogt zenen geshtanen

00:16:28.580 --> 00:16:29.870
dort in droysn

00:16:29.870 --> 00:16:33.140
un zey hobn gezen, m'hot gevorfn. s'iz ummeglekh gevezn, farshteystu

00:16:33.140 --> 00:16:34.180
az vi s'iz meglekh

00:16:34.180 --> 00:16:35.726
himl faln tsu der erd tsu zen

00:16:35.726 --> 00:16:37.736
nor ikh bin dokh gevezn in shpitol.

00:16:37.736 --> 00:16:40.076
ikh hob gezen vi m'hot aruntergevorfn di kinder.

00:16:41.458 --> 00:16:46.256
un m'hot genumen di eltere. iz geven a shvester, HARA, SARA hot zi geheysn rikhtik

00:16:46.256 --> 00:16:48.736
SARA WEINTRAUB UNK

00:16:48.736 --> 00:16:52.226
iz gevezn, hot zikh moyre gekrign, iz zi arayn, farshteystu.

00:16:52.226 --> 00:16:53.960
dos toyer hot zikh geefnt, iz zi geven UNK

00:16:53.960 --> 00:16:55.860
shtign aroyftsugeyn azoy

00:16:55.903 --> 00:16:59.891
un s'iz gevezn a toyer, vos m'hot ge- arayngefirt di meysim mit di kranke.

00:16:59.891 --> 00:17:05.351
dos toyer hot zikh geefnt azoy ara- ineveynik. iz zi iz an- hot moyre gekrign, az zi iz antlofn UNK bahaltn do

00:17:05.351 --> 00:17:08.161
un d- untn iz geshtanen a yidisher vakh politsey

00:17:08.627 --> 00:17:10.275
a vakh a yidisher

00:17:10.939 --> 00:17:15.607
hot der, der zelber F- der zelber GE- GESTAPO, sh- UNK heyst er, der BOKSER

00:17:15.984 --> 00:17:17.311
hot dos gezen

00:17:17.385 --> 00:17:19.215
hot er gekhapt dem politsyant

00:17:19.215 --> 00:17:23.385
un hot im gegebn a va- a ra- a khap on ⟨in dem⟩, un m'hot UNK aroyfgevorfn dem politsyant v-

00:17:23.385 --> 00:17:24.595
er hot zi bahaltn, zogt er.

00:17:24.595 --> 00:17:28.061
oyfgevorfn oyf dem vogn vos m'hot gefirt ale alte mit ⟨alts⟩ tsunezamen.

00:17:28.061 --> 00:17:29.461
un di shvester

00:17:29.856 --> 00:17:31.689
iz, iz zi, hot er aroysgelozt.

00:17:31.982 --> 00:17:34.963
dos geven. dos hob ikh gezen mit mayne eygene oygn.

00:17:35.138 --> 00:17:36.246
farshteystu.

00:17:36.859 --> 00:17:40.481
yetst zog ikh, kh'hob shoyn gezen dem sof vos tut zikh, bin ikh gelofn vayter

00:17:40.740 --> 00:17:43.214
⟨zog ikh⟩ ikh vil nisht zayn do oykh nisht. kh'hob shoyn moyre.

00:17:43.930 --> 00:17:46.236
iz in eyn molt iz do an oyfruf

00:17:46.731 --> 00:17:51.146
az me zukht elektriker, tekhniker, enzhinirer, azoy un azoy

00:17:51.912 --> 00:17:53.912
bin ikh gelofn tsu dem

00:17:53.912 --> 00:17:57.772
er, er iz gevezn der UNK fun di ELEKTROWNIA oykh, fun, nokh dem fun PIOTRKOW a INZYNIER

00:17:57.772 --> 00:18:00.302
fun sh- Lodzh meyn ikh, INZYNIER

00:18:00.302 --> 00:18:01.541
VAYNBERG

00:18:01.800 --> 00:18:03.190
hob ikh gezogt tsun im "her oys

00:18:03.190 --> 00:18:06.570
du host mikh" hot er mir gegebn, ikh hob dos lign bizn hayntikn tog, beyde

00:18:06.570 --> 00:18:08.740
hob ikh a papir fun INZYNIER VAYNBERG

00:18:08.740 --> 00:18:09.590
UNK

00:18:09.590 --> 00:18:11.130
fir hundert fertsn

00:18:11.402 --> 00:18:13.792
iz ⟨NADAJESZE⟩ DO TRAMWAJU

00:18:13.792 --> 00:18:16.262
iz PRACOWAL ⟨PRZEDWONI⟩ UNK ELEKTRIKA TUTEM

00:18:16.330 --> 00:18:18.175
dos iz fun INZYNIER VAYNBERG.

00:18:18.175 --> 00:18:20.984
di tsveyte bin ikh gelofn tsu INZYNIER DAWIDOWICZ

00:18:20.984 --> 00:18:24.915
un gezogt "do host" ⟨iz⟩ hot er mir gegebn. ikh hob fun DAWIDOWICZn di zelbe.

00:18:24.915 --> 00:18:27.345
er hot mir geshribn ⟨NAJDALSZE⟩. mit UNK

00:18:27.345 --> 00:18:30.127
hot men mikh arayngelozt oyfn BALUTER plats

00:18:30.471 --> 00:18:34.903
un ikh h- zol geyn arayn meldn zikh dort. bin arayngekumen dort, hob mikh gemoldn

00:18:35.297 --> 00:18:39.993
ver zitst dort? zitst der direktor ⟨SCHEID⟩ vos er iz gevezn bay der ⟨R.E.G.⟩

00:18:39.993 --> 00:18:41.723
er iz gevorn der hoypt

00:18:41.723 --> 00:18:42.547
man

00:18:42.942 --> 00:18:45.284
fun di gantse geto fun di ayznban

00:18:45.284 --> 00:18:47.258
un fun di STRASSENBAHN.

00:18:47.258 --> 00:18:49.888
dort iz gezitsn BIEBOW un der ⟨prezes⟩.

00:18:50.839 --> 00:18:53.924
zogt er "vos makhstu do?" hob ikh im gezogt ⟨vos ikh zog dir⟩.

