vos zenen gevezn in far ⟨WEILAND⟩ in ⟨A.K.B.⟩

00:28:27.930 --> 00:28:29.291
hob ikh zey tsugenumen.

00:28:29.753 --> 00:28:33.527
mit eyn mol, farshteystu, iz g- iz gevezn, WIR hobn gehat ⟨di⟩ tramvay

00:28:33.567 --> 00:28:37.864
un s- in di geto iz gevezn a, s'heyst a apteylung, transport apteylung.

00:28:38.224 --> 00:28:39.331
KLEINMAN.

00:28:40.148 --> 00:28:45.035
er hot gearbet, farshteyt ir, transport, hot gearbet mit dem, mit dem ⟨WEILAND⟩

00:28:45.227 --> 00:28:47.516
mit dem A.K.B.

00:28:49.125 --> 00:28:50.396
vos hot pasirt?

00:28:50.396 --> 00:28:53.560
mit eyn minut iz geganen, hot tsugenumen, s'iz gekumen der t-

00:28:53.560 --> 00:28:54.670
di l- ratsye

00:28:54.670 --> 00:28:56.430
vos iz arayngekumen far undz

00:28:56.430 --> 00:29:00.970
iz geganen, hot tsugenumen di ratsye far di hundert zeks un fertsik mentshn vos zey hobn gekrign far shvere ⟨arbeter⟩ yede vokh.

00:29:00.970 --> 00:29:02.030
tsugenumen.

00:29:02.030 --> 00:29:03.649
mir hobn nisht gekrign di ratsye.

00:29:03.688 --> 00:29:05.423
mentshn ⟨heybn on⟩ tsu shrayen, "vos iz"?

00:29:05.423 --> 00:29:06.416
UNK

00:29:08.548 --> 00:29:09.676
dertseylt

00:29:08.734 --> 00:29:11.360
u- un mentshn UNK shrayen "vos tut zikh do?"

00:29:11.383 --> 00:29:13.436
ahin un aher, farshteystu

00:29:13.662 --> 00:29:15.698
iz geganen, farshteystu, m'hot gemakht

00:29:15.737 --> 00:29:21.488
az m'hot getsvungen az der transport mit di elektrishe STRASSENBAHN zol vern eyns.

00:29:21.488 --> 00:29:23.915
der direktor iz gekumen tsu forn, ⟨SCHEID⟩

00:29:23.955 --> 00:29:27.968
zogt er "ikh bin nisht, ikh hob" zogt er "mit UNK iz ⟨gar⟩ nisht tsu THUN.

00:29:27.968 --> 00:29:31.509
ICH, DASS iz elektrishe STRASSENBAHN, un du zolst mer dos nisht makhn.

00:29:31.600 --> 00:29:34.050
nor alnfal, farshteyst, iz geganen oyf azan oyfn

00:29:34.050 --> 00:29:35.020
hot men fareynikt

00:29:35.020 --> 00:29:36.080
az zey zoln nemen

00:29:36.080 --> 00:29:37.660
oykh tsu far zayne mentshn

00:29:37.660 --> 00:29:38.950
zoln kenen oykh nemen

00:29:38.950 --> 00:29:40.683
zoln di UNK grablers nemen

00:29:40.683 --> 00:29:42.529
un m'hot zikh fareynikt. s'iz gevorn

00:29:42.737 --> 00:29:43.991
a transport

00:29:43.991 --> 00:29:47.060
di elektrishe ⟨STRASSENBAHNS⟩ transport fareynikt.
